:: ============================================================
:: KEYS FILE TEMPLATE - Kids Korner / Buddy Lounge
:: ============================================================
:: 1. COPY this file and rename the copy to:  keys.local.bat
:: 2. Paste your real keys below (get them via Buddy-Vault\vault.html)
:: 3. keys.local.bat is protected by .gitignore - it will NEVER
::    be uploaded to GitHub or seen by anyone you share this with.
:: NEVER put real keys in this .example file or any other file!
:: ============================================================

:: Chat AI (free models) - https://openrouter.ai/keys
:: (example key shown - replace with your real one)
set OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-your-api-key-here

:: Lifelike voice, optional - https://elevenlabs.io
:: set ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
:: set ELEVENLABS_VOICE_ID=21m00Tcm4TlvDq8ikWAM

:: Different chat model, optional
:: set BUDDY_MODEL=poolside/laguna-m.1:free

:: Age tier for SMS texters, optional (default 12 = family-safe)
:: set BUDDY_SMS_AGE=12
